name: Esf
body:
## esf


### Install

```npm install esf --save```

### Usage

```js
import { combine } from 'esf'
或者
import * as esf from 'esf'
esf.combine()
```

### API

[API DOC](https://github.com/dyygtfx/esf/wiki/API-Doc)

### Test

```npm test```
